  "id": "RAW_f23977d2",
  "title": "马斯克转发 Kimi 论文引起硅谷大讨论，Attention 下一个战场是什么？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mjc1NjM3MjY2MA==&mid=2691566064&idx=1&sn=9b3a1846128b388ab8cd5809e132470f",
  "date": "2026-03-20 07:06:00",
